I found it quite interesting seeing as how this is the only footage out there that has sufficient proof of what really goes on during these secret "political meetings". For those of you who have no idea what this is, take a look here: http://www.infowars.com/bg1.html. This video is long but its quite entertaining toward the end. After you watch it, post your views on this situation.
